message.content: cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MED, cs.NEURON - The paper deals with medical image segmentation using deep learning, which falls under the computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG) categories. The use of Bayesian neural networks and uncertainty quantification also suggests a focus on artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and neural networks (cs.NEURON). Finally, the application of the method to tumour volume estimation in a medical context suggests a potential fit for the medical informatics (cs.MED) category.
